#: class-gf-paypal.php:1670
msgid "The payment is pending because you are not yet verified. You must verify your account before you can accept this payment."
msgstr "The payment is pending because you are not yet verified. You must verify your account before you can accept this payment."

#: class-gf-paypal.php:1667
msgid "The payment is pending because it was made via credit card and you must upgrade your account to Business or Premier status in order to receive the funds. Upgrade can also mean that you have reached the monthly limit for transactions on your account."
msgstr "The payment is pending because it was made via credit card and you must upgrade your account to Business or Premier status in order to receive the funds. Upgrade can also mean that you have reached the monthly limit for transactions on your account."

#: class-gf-paypal.php:1664
msgid "The payment is pending because it was made to an email address that is not yet registered or confirmed."
msgstr "The payment is pending because it was made to an email address that is not yet registered or confirmed."

#: class-gf-paypal.php:1661
msgid "The payment is pending while it is being reviewed by PayPal for risk."
msgstr "The payment is pending while it is being reviewed by PayPal for risk."

#: class-gf-paypal.php:1658
msgid "You set the payment action to Order and have not yet captured funds."
msgstr "You set the payment action to Order and have not yet captured funds."

#: class-gf-paypal.php:1655
msgid "You do not have a balance in the currency sent, and you do not have your Payment Receiving Preferences set to automatically convert and accept this payment. You must manually accept or deny this payment."
msgstr "You do not have a balance in the currency sent, and you do not have your Payment Receiving Preferences set to automatically convert and accept this payment. You must manually accept or deny this payment."

#: class-gf-paypal.php:1652
msgid "The payment is pending because you hold a non-U.S. account and do not have a withdrawal mechanism. You must manually accept or deny this payment from your Account Overview."
msgstr "The payment is pending because you hold a non-U.S. account and do not have a withdrawal mechanism. You must manually accept or deny this payment from your Account Overview."

#: class-gf-paypal.php:1649
msgid "The payment is pending because it was made by an eCheck that has not yet cleared."
msgstr "The payment is pending because it was made by an eCheck that has not yet cleared."

#: class-gf-paypal.php:1646
msgid "You set the payment action to Authorization and have not yet captured funds."
msgstr "You set the payment action to Authorisation and have not yet captured funds."

#: class-gf-paypal.php:1643
msgid "The payment is pending because your customer did not include a confirmed shipping address and your Payment Receiving Preferences are set to allow you to manually accept or deny each of these payments. To change your preference, go to the Preferences section of your Profile."
msgstr "The payment is pending because your customer did not include a confirmed shipping address and your Payment Receiving Preferences are set to allow you to manually accept or deny each of these payments. To change your preference, go to the Preferences section of your Profile."

#: class-gf-paypal.php:1611 class-gf-paypal.php:1673 class-gf-paypal.php:1676
